Class ReferenceFactory

java.lang.Object
org.nasdanika.emf.persistence.ReferenceFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
ObjectFactory<List<?>>
public class ReferenceFactory extends Object implements ObjectFactory<List<?>>
Creates reference value/element - EObject or proxy. May create zero or more elements for filesets and resourcesets.
